  "detailed_description": "<strong>                                         Run!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/ef61a602e1611cdbb594f078eab8b290.poster.avif?t=1741697361\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/ef61a602e1611cdbb594f078eab8b290.webm?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>                                         Catch!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/b145c7ef4cf7c99fb0af6e1be0a2a58e.poster.avif?t=1741697361\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/b145c7ef4cf7c99fb0af6e1be0a2a58e.webm?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/b145c7ef4cf7c99fb0af6e1be0a2a58e.mp4?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tag Hop is a fast-paced movement based parkour PvP game combining bunny hop & other advanced movement mechanics with simple playground Tag. <br>Run away and dodge chasers with advanced movement.<br>Or catch runners with route predictions. Just like Tag in real life.<br><br>Join discussions about Tag Hop on r/TagHop and join the community  Discord server to be the first to see new content, as well as being a part of the development process of Tag Hop!<br><br>And most importantly:<br><strong>Have fun!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/39931ab41cf337415b84939fe2cf26d2.poster.avif?t=1741697361\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/39931ab41cf337415b84939fe2cf26d2.webm?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/39931ab41cf337415b84939fe2cf26d2.mp4?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game modes</strong></h2>Tag Hop includes 4 different game modes: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Playground/Classic Tag<br></li><li>  Infected<br></li><li>  Points Tag<br></li><li>  Elimination</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Dedicated servers<br></li><li>  Smooth movement: bunnyhop, diving, surfing, advanced crouch techniques.<br></li><li>  Competitive & casual lobbies<br></li><li>  Rooftops styled environments<br></li><li>  Extra content: grayblock maps</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>                                         Run!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/ef61a602e1611cdbb594f078eab8b290.poster.avif?t=1741697361\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/ef61a602e1611cdbb594f078eab8b290.webm?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>                                         Catch!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/b145c7ef4cf7c99fb0af6e1be0a2a58e.poster.avif?t=1741697361\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/b145c7ef4cf7c99fb0af6e1be0a2a58e.webm?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/b145c7ef4cf7c99fb0af6e1be0a2a58e.mp4?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Tag Hop is a fast-paced movement based parkour PvP game combining bunny hop & other advanced movement mechanics with simple playground Tag. <br>Run away and dodge chasers with advanced movement.<br>Or catch runners with route predictions. Just like Tag in real life.<br><br>Join discussions about Tag Hop on r/TagHop and join the community  Discord server to be the first to see new content, as well as being a part of the development process of Tag Hop!<br><br>And most importantly:<br><strong>Have fun!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/39931ab41cf337415b84939fe2cf26d2.poster.avif?t=1741697361\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/39931ab41cf337415b84939fe2cf26d2.webm?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625330/extras/39931ab41cf337415b84939fe2cf26d2.mp4?t=1741697361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game modes</strong></h2>Tag Hop includes 4 different game modes: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Playground/Classic Tag<br></li><li>  Infected<br></li><li>  Points Tag<br></li><li>  Elimination</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Dedicated servers<br></li><li>  Smooth movement: bunnyhop, diving, surfing, advanced crouch techniques.<br></li><li>  Competitive & casual lobbies<br></li><li>  Rooftops styled environments<br></li><li>  Extra content: grayblock maps</li></ul>",
